WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes‚Ä¶

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 40]

02:50.560 --> 02:51.840
I just want to complete

02:51.840 --> 02:53.950
what was left unfinished 60,000 years ago.

02:53.980 --> 02:55.980
So, whether you are Xing Yue or not,

02:56.000 --> 02:57.410
just for that face of yours,

02:57.440 --> 02:59.040
I must marry you.

03:00.940 --> 03:02.300
You have no choice.

03:03.250 --> 03:05.000
Before I say yes,

03:05.020 --> 03:06.570
I want a promise from you.

03:06.640 --> 03:07.590
Go ahead.

03:08.270 --> 03:11.070
You must never harm any living being in this world again.

03:11.090 --> 03:13.850
Since killing them is so easy for you,

03:13.880 --> 03:15.890
why bother with such boring acts?

03:19.680 --> 03:21.579
If you're negotiating with me as the wife

03:21.600 --> 03:22.880
of the Hidden Lord,

03:23.850 --> 03:25.079
I will comply with your terms.

03:25.100 --> 03:25.820
Alright.

03:26.570 --> 03:27.450
I promise you.

03:32.829 --> 03:34.140
Tomorrow,

03:34.780 --> 03:35.900
the Lunar Hidden Sea

03:36.520 --> 03:38.290
will be our wedding venue.

03:39.780 --> 03:41.680
The Lunar Hidden Sea has long disappeared.

03:42.360 --> 03:43.940
60,000 years ago,

03:44.290 --> 03:45.940
Jing Yuan could replicate Xing Yue Pavilion

03:46.000 --> 03:48.360
for Xing Yue in the Demon Race's territory.

03:48.720 --> 03:50.400
Likewise, here in the Eastern Continent,

03:50.420 --> 03:51.910
I can replicate the Lunar Hidden Sea for you.

03:53.060 --> 03:55.180
I want everything

03:55.210 --> 03:57.490
to be exactly as it was 60,000 years ago.

04:17.420 --> 04:18.390
Master,

04:19.050 --> 04:20.579
Bai Shuo was right.

04:21.459 --> 04:23.780
Everyone has their own responsibilities to fulfil.

04:25.040 --> 04:27.070
For the future of the Fox Clan,

04:27.460 --> 04:28.790
Mu Jiu sacrificed himself;

04:29.340 --> 04:32.170
To settle old grudges,

04:32.190 --> 04:33.590
Cang Shan gave his life;

04:34.490 --> 04:36.659
To protect the Polar Region,

04:37.140 --> 04:38.530
you hurt yourself.

04:40.080 --> 04:41.880
To protect the world, Bai Shuo bravely went

04:42.880 --> 04:44.480
to face the danger.

04:45.900 --> 04:47.010
And I...

04:48.190 --> 04:50.240
have my own things to do.

06:05.950 --> 06:07.510
This wedding gown

06:08.500 --> 06:10.800
is exactly the same as the one from 60,000 years ago.

06:12.400 --> 06:13.540
Try it on.

06:19.850 --> 06:21.360
You'll wear it eventually.

06:21.950 --> 06:24.680
Whether it's marrying you or taking control of the world,

06:24.700 --> 06:27.210
I will reclaim everything I've lost.

06:28.620 --> 06:29.940
Stop it.

06:30.230 --> 06:31.870
What's the meaning of all this?

06:32.570 --> 06:33.520
The meaning?

06:33.740 --> 06:36.130
I'm the meaning of this world, aren't I?

06:36.150 --> 06:37.840
If you keep being so arrogant,

06:37.870 --> 06:40.820
you will never understand the true love and sincerity of this world.

06:40.840 --> 06:43.050
Even if you possess 10,000 years of divine power,

06:43.080 --> 06:44.590
it's all just emptiness.

06:44.870 --> 06:45.750
Only the weak

06:45.750 --> 06:48.159
chase after those meaningless meanings.

06:48.330 --> 06:50.570
My Divine Mirror reflects all things.

06:50.600 --> 06:53.070
It can also see all the evil thoughts in the world.

06:53.090 --> 06:54.580
Whether it's Eternals,

06:54.610 --> 06:57.050
demons, humans, or the Outlanders,

06:57.070 --> 06:58.090
all beings

06:58.130 --> 07:00.020
have their selfish and ugly sides.

07:00.050 --> 07:01.190
It was like this 60,000 years ago,

07:01.220 --> 07:02.560
and it will be the same 60,000 years later.

07:02.580 --> 07:03.900
Time will not make it

07:03.930 --> 07:05.240
any better.

07:05.260 --> 07:07.070
Is this the meaning you want?

07:07.810 --> 07:09.730
In this world, both good and evil exist.

07:10.410 --> 07:12.060
Good has meaning

07:12.710 --> 07:14.390
only in the face of evil.

07:15.650 --> 07:17.640
I won't waste words with you.

07:18.080 --> 07:19.490
After tomorrow's wedding,

07:19.510 --> 07:21.730
you will be my Divine Queen.

07:22.030 --> 07:23.910
All the good and evil in this world

07:23.930 --> 07:25.970
will no longer have anything to do with you.

07:34.110 --> 07:36.220
Don't struggle in vain.

07:37.060 --> 07:38.800
You have lost all your five Contemplations and divine power,

07:38.800 --> 07:39.980
leaving you weak.

07:40.240 --> 07:42.000
You can't stir up any more trouble.

08:51.440 --> 08:52.770
Tian Huo?

08:53.910 --> 08:55.380
Master, you're awake.

08:55.410 --> 08:56.220
Where is Bai Shuo?

08:58.550 --> 09:00.200
Xing Yue Divine Arrow has been repaired.

09:13.190 --> 09:14.610
How?

09:14.690 --> 09:15.690
This time,

09:16.140 --> 09:18.050
I didn't report to you in advance.

09:19.380 --> 09:21.400
Will you blame me?

09:31.340 --> 09:32.410
Tian Huo!

09:37.990 --> 09:38.820
Tian Huo,

09:38.850 --> 09:39.920
what's wrong with you?

09:46.060 --> 09:47.940
Why do you have no spiritual power at all?

09:48.660 --> 09:49.750
back then,

09:50.530 --> 09:52.290
when the first King of Outlanders

09:53.370 --> 09:55.960
saw the remnants of the Divine Arrow,

09:57.030 --> 09:59.810
he forged the Outlander King's Sword with his own blood.

10:00.510 --> 10:01.720
For a thousand years,

10:02.330 --> 10:04.400
only the Hua bloodline

10:04.580 --> 10:06.750
could pull out the Outlander King's Sword

10:06.780 --> 10:08.270
and infuse it with life.

10:08.290 --> 10:09.960
Now that the Outlander King's Sword is broken,

10:09.990 --> 10:11.230
I think

10:11.970 --> 10:15.230
only the spiritual blood of the Hua bloodline

10:16.030 --> 10:18.240
can restore the broken sword.

10:22.370 --> 10:23.260
It's okay.

10:23.740 --> 10:25.160
I... I'll save you.

10:27.930 --> 10:28.990
Master,

10:29.170 --> 10:30.710
don't waste your power.

10:31.210 --> 10:33.280
This is my own choice.

10:33.300 --> 10:34.510
I can save you.

10:34.540 --> 10:35.620
Master,

10:35.640 --> 10:36.640
it won't work.

10:36.670 --> 10:37.970
It'll work! I can save you!

10:38.000 --> 10:38.890
Master.

10:39.800 --> 10:42.410
I also have my own mission.

10:43.110 --> 10:44.920
As the Outlanders' princess,

10:45.860 --> 10:47.920
I've been enjoying respect and honor since I was young,

10:50.140 --> 10:51.890
but not once have I

10:53.850 --> 10:56.380
shouldered the responsibilities that come with it.

10:57.140 --> 10:58.480
This time,

10:58.780 --> 11:00.690
I finally...

11:00.720 --> 11:04.740
I finally did the right thing.

11:11.340 --> 11:12.580
Bai Shuo...

11:12.790 --> 11:14.620
She went to the Cold Spring Palace.

11:14.910 --> 11:16.750
She didn't want me to tell you,

11:16.780 --> 11:18.240
but I know that

11:18.270 --> 11:21.450
if something were to happen to her,

11:22.840 --> 11:24.960
it would be a regret

11:25.620 --> 11:27.560
you would carry forever.

11:28.210 --> 11:29.300
Master,

11:29.730 --> 11:30.960
this journey

11:32.810 --> 11:34.670
has been so difficult.

11:35.280 --> 11:37.170
So many have already left us.

11:37.920 --> 11:40.650
Take the Divine Arrow and save her now.

11:41.710 --> 11:44.040
Don't leave any regrets.

11:54.850 --> 11:56.500
I'll leave these two

11:57.720 --> 12:00.260
to you for safekeeping.

12:06.050 --> 12:07.370
Don't be sad.

12:09.100 --> 12:10.280
I am just...

12:11.740 --> 12:13.850
going to find them.

12:16.620 --> 12:17.960
In this life,

12:20.220 --> 12:23.260
being able to follow you...

12:25.110 --> 12:26.420
leaves me...

12:28.490 --> 12:29.780
with no regrets.

12:30.040 --> 12:33.510
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

12:34.210 --> 12:37.410
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

12:38.010 --> 12:41.390
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

12:42.080 --> 12:44.790
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

12:45.210 --> 12:48.670
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

12:49.050 --> 12:52.230
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

12:52.760 --> 12:56.000
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

12:57.340 --> 12:59.830
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

13:00.700 --> 13:04.170
‚ôęAnother year passed‚ôę

13:08.060 --> 13:11.180
‚ôęAnother year passed‚ôę

13:41.490 --> 13:43.150
When the Heavenly Bell stops,

13:43.980 --> 13:45.280
a grand ceremony should be held.

13:54.450 --> 13:55.950
I've been waiting

13:56.390 --> 13:58.510
for this couple's bow for 60,000 years.

14:10.740 --> 14:11.980
The Purple Moon?

14:12.250 --> 14:13.870
You have lost all your five Contemplations and divine power.

14:13.870 --> 14:15.010
With such a mortal body,

14:15.120 --> 14:17.390
why can you wield the Purple Lunar Power of Jing Yuan?

14:17.410 --> 14:20.260
Because I have reestablished the divine pact with Fan Yue.

14:20.390 --> 14:22.230
Of course, we can wield what belongs to each other.

14:26.230 --> 14:27.230
Fan Yue,

14:28.440 --> 14:30.280
forgive me for leaving alone.

14:31.100 --> 14:32.720
But before I leave,

14:33.380 --> 14:35.660
I need to borrow something from you.

14:36.180 --> 14:37.730
You will support me,

14:37.750 --> 14:38.520
right?

15:06.030 --> 15:07.300
You should know

15:07.570 --> 15:09.090
you're just a mortal now,

15:09.110 --> 15:10.510
not a deity.

15:10.540 --> 15:12.210
What you've been cultivating all along is Eternal magic.

15:12.240 --> 15:14.180
Now, you've forcibly channeled demonic power into your body.

15:14.470 --> 15:15.360
Even a deity

15:15.360 --> 15:17.250
cannot merge Eternal power with demonic power.

15:17.270 --> 15:18.930
From now on,

15:19.200 --> 15:21.130
you will be tortured by the evil aura every day.

15:21.750 --> 15:23.230
For those ants,

15:23.250 --> 15:24.550
for killing me,

15:24.980 --> 15:26.240
you've turned yourself into a creature

15:26.270 --> 15:28.270
that is neither human, nor Eternal, nor demon.

15:28.690 --> 15:30.210
Is it worth it?

15:30.490 --> 15:32.010
I am not Xing Yue,

15:32.500 --> 15:34.580
nor have I ever thought of becoming a deity.

15:34.610 --> 15:36.000
I am not like her,

15:36.160 --> 15:38.110
born to bring peace to the world.

15:38.130 --> 15:39.580
What I've always wanted

15:39.700 --> 15:40.930
was simply to protect

15:40.960 --> 15:42.040
the people I love and cherish.

15:42.350 --> 15:44.750
But now, the people I love and cherish

15:44.770 --> 15:46.410
have all died or been hurt because of you.

15:46.440 --> 15:47.250
If I don't kill you,

15:47.270 --> 15:50.030
what meaning will my life have,

15:50.060 --> 15:51.380
even if I live on in peace?

15:51.400 --> 15:52.750
I will let you know

15:53.870 --> 15:55.430
that the love and cherishing

15:56.020 --> 15:57.070
you think you have

15:57.120 --> 15:58.510
are all false!

15:58.510 --> 15:59.990
I am the strongest in the world.

16:00.010 --> 16:02.110
Even if I betray the world and kill everyone,

16:02.140 --> 16:04.520
I still love you!

16:04.720 --> 16:06.460
But why?

16:07.250 --> 16:08.760
It has been 60,000 years,

16:10.260 --> 16:13.270
and you've always treated my heart like worthless trash

16:13.270 --> 16:15.150
and never treasured it even for a moment!

16:15.660 --> 16:17.560
Love is not just about receiving.

16:18.180 --> 16:19.890
Love is also about sacrifice.

16:20.410 --> 16:21.300
It's about giving.

16:21.720 --> 16:24.570
But everything you do is murder and possession.

16:24.670 --> 16:27.240
What you do is only to satisfy your own selfish desires.

16:27.600 --> 16:28.600
Mo Li,

16:29.550 --> 16:31.440
you don't have a true heart,

16:31.960 --> 16:33.240
and you don't know love.

16:33.870 --> 16:35.600
If I can drag you and Hidden Heart to death with me,

16:35.600 --> 16:36.790
then today,

16:37.210 --> 16:39.450
even if I die here,

16:39.470 --> 16:40.750
it would be worth it.

16:54.020 --> 16:55.750
I did nothing wrong.

16:56.260 --> 16:58.140
It's the world that is foolish.

17:16.390 --> 17:17.319
Fan Yue?

17:31.260 --> 17:32.890
You fixed the arrow?

17:33.120 --> 17:34.190
Tian Huo did it.

17:34.730 --> 17:36.310
She sacrificed herself to the arrow

17:36.510 --> 17:37.870
and recasted it.

17:39.550 --> 17:41.380
The Xing Yue Divine Bow has long been destroyed.

17:41.400 --> 17:42.880
How did you find it?

17:43.180 --> 17:44.650
The Divine Bow reappeared in the world

17:44.680 --> 17:45.880
because of you.

17:45.990 --> 17:47.740
Fu Ling is the bow spirit of the Divine Bow.

17:48.340 --> 17:49.210
When she died,

17:49.850 --> 17:51.020
the Divine Bow appeared.

17:54.190 --> 17:56.440
No wonder she could hurt me.

17:56.660 --> 17:57.870
Heaven,

17:57.900 --> 17:59.860
you really are cunning.

18:00.050 --> 18:02.410
You actually made the bow spirit of the Divine Bow fall in love with Chong Zhao.

18:02.670 --> 18:04.280
You think that with such a bond,

18:04.300 --> 18:05.850
you can stop me?

18:07.100 --> 18:08.430
Dream on.

18:09.070 --> 18:10.270
You keep saying

18:10.290 --> 18:11.450
that I don't know love

18:11.480 --> 18:12.650
and I deserve to die.

18:13.120 --> 18:15.950
Today, I will let you see with your own eyes

18:15.970 --> 18:18.420
how foolish so-called true love

18:18.450 --> 18:19.920
and sacrifice are?

18:26.890 --> 18:27.700
How could it be?

18:33.890 --> 18:35.110
60,000 years ago,

18:35.110 --> 18:37.740
I fell beneath the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

18:37.890 --> 18:39.310
Do you think that after 60,000 years,

18:39.310 --> 18:40.510
I still don't have a way

18:40.510 --> 18:41.790
to deal with this one and only divine weapon

18:41.790 --> 18:43.510
that could threaten me?

18:43.700 --> 18:45.850
My Hidden power is even stronger than before.

18:46.070 --> 18:47.920
And you are just a mortal.

18:48.730 --> 18:50.770
The mere Xing Yue Divine Bow

18:51.680 --> 18:53.670
can no longer hurt me.

19:10.610 --> 19:11.610
Chong Zhao!

19:11.640 --> 19:12.880
What are you doing?

19:25.090 --> 19:26.340
Chong Zhao,

19:26.750 --> 19:29.290
you actually managed to stop me from entering my sea of consciousness?

19:29.410 --> 19:30.990
Shuo! Fan Yue!

19:31.450 --> 19:32.660
It's Zhao.

19:32.990 --> 19:35.030
Zhao, wake up!

19:40.710 --> 19:42.280
You've always been arrogant and conceited,

19:42.310 --> 19:44.350
which is why you forgot a saying in this world:

19:44.380 --> 19:45.860
"Lie in wait to deceive the enemy,

19:45.880 --> 19:47.530
store up strength to wait for the right moment."

19:47.560 --> 19:49.080
I indeed can't kill you

19:49.100 --> 19:50.650
and can't leave the sea of consciousness.

19:50.680 --> 19:52.130
But if I exhaust my Eternal power,

19:52.160 --> 19:53.550
I can still hold you off for a while.

19:53.570 --> 19:54.650
Chong Zhao!

19:54.740 --> 19:56.280
What are you doing?

20:00.920 --> 20:01.810
Shuo,

20:01.830 --> 20:03.510
I've survived this long

20:03.540 --> 20:05.670
because Xi was still alive at that time.

20:05.690 --> 20:06.690
I once had an unrealistic hope,

20:06.720 --> 20:08.880
wanting to reclaim my body and be with her.

20:09.150 --> 20:11.560
I know my death can only severely wound Mo Li

20:11.580 --> 20:13.070
and can't kill him.

20:13.270 --> 20:15.380
So after Xi died, I've been waiting.

20:15.110 --> 20:19.400
‚ôęNo matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once‚ôę

20:15.880 --> 20:18.410
I've been waiting for a chance to give him a fatal blow.

20:19.120 --> 20:20.560
Now, I've got it.

20:21.650 --> 20:26.980
‚ôęBecause love is thrilling‚ôę

20:25.220 --> 20:26.910
My death will be worth it.

20:27.620 --> 20:31.120
‚ôęIf you tear open my heart‚ôę

20:27.920 --> 20:29.050
Shuo,

20:29.070 --> 20:30.070
Fan Yue,

20:30.100 --> 20:31.990
don't show any mercy.

20:31.920 --> 20:34.230
‚ôęI can hold you a little tighter‚ôę

20:32.210 --> 20:33.030
Remember,

20:34.190 --> 20:35.710
kill Mo Li,

20:34.780 --> 20:39.220
‚ôęThis pain will gradually fade‚ôę

20:36.500 --> 20:37.710
and save the world!

20:41.840 --> 20:45.430
‚ôęTime withers the moonlight‚ôę

20:45.910 --> 20:48.390
‚ôęAll that's left is pitch darkness‚ôę

20:48.790 --> 20:50.550
‚ôęI want to tear apart‚ôę

20:51.580 --> 20:54.230
‚ôęThis sky for you‚ôę

20:55.160 --> 20:57.320
‚ôęA lifetime of guarding everything with you‚ôę

20:57.940 --> 21:01.340
‚ôęCrossing the abyss to fulfill our vow‚ôę

21:01.500 --> 21:02.450
Zhao!

21:02.060 --> 21:05.130
‚ôęI'll leap without a thought for tomorrow‚ôę

21:05.740 --> 21:08.230
‚ôęThis moment feels like forever‚ôę

21:08.450 --> 21:11.510
‚ôęI've missed too much time in my life‚ôę

21:11.910 --> 21:15.370
‚ôęI'll throw myself into this flame for you‚ôę

21:15.920 --> 21:17.910
‚ôęEven if I'll perish‚ôę

21:17.960 --> 21:20.510
‚ôęAt least I can still kiss your face‚ôę

21:20.960 --> 21:24.220
‚ôęBurn out my waning moon‚ôę

21:24.980 --> 21:32.720
‚ôęIn exchange for a lifetime of passion‚ôę

21:31.510 --> 21:32.310
Zhao.

22:03.770 --> 22:04.720
Mo Li,

22:05.940 --> 22:06.980
you've lost.

22:07.890 --> 22:09.730
In the end,

22:10.100 --> 22:12.300
sacrifice defeated your evil.

22:17.420 --> 22:19.040
Do you think

22:19.440 --> 22:22.030
I would die so easily?

22:33.700 --> 22:35.560
Back then, even Xing Yue and Jing Yuan

22:35.590 --> 22:38.430
couldn't destroy my Hidden Heart with the Xing Yue Bow.

22:38.790 --> 22:41.070
Do you think you can do it?

22:42.020 --> 22:44.270
Now, I've grown even stronger.

22:44.800 --> 22:46.480
Chong Zhao is dead,

22:46.500 --> 22:48.720
and this body is about to vanish.

22:49.120 --> 22:51.840
Then I will use the power of the entire world

22:51.860 --> 22:54.100
to rebuild my divine body!

22:58.330 --> 22:59.810
The Hidden Heart?

23:51.180 --> 23:52.050
Fan Yue!

24:15.000 --> 24:16.460
Even if you use yourself as the vessel,

24:16.920 --> 24:18.930
you still can't trap me!

24:19.980 --> 24:21.300
For me,

24:21.320 --> 24:22.560
nothing is impossible.

24:22.590 --> 24:23.690
It's just

24:23.720 --> 24:25.300
a matter of destroying both you and me!

24:28.320 --> 24:29.230
Fan Yue!

24:30.080 --> 24:31.430
What are you doing?

24:31.710 --> 24:32.910
Stop it!

24:33.300 --> 24:34.170
Shuo,

24:34.600 --> 24:35.880
do you still remember

24:36.170 --> 24:38.140
the promise you made to me

24:38.200 --> 24:39.930
on the cliff in the Polar Region?

24:42.490 --> 24:44.750
I'll take care of Bright Moon Palace for you.

24:46.060 --> 24:47.860
I'll accompany Tian Huo.

24:48.930 --> 24:50.690
I'll go and see

24:52.380 --> 24:54.720
every mountain and river on the Eastern Continent,

24:56.700 --> 24:59.280
guarding every star, sun, and moon.

25:01.450 --> 25:02.450
I promise you.

25:04.700 --> 25:05.860
You said

25:08.940 --> 25:10.960
you'd never leave me alone again.

25:12.210 --> 25:13.950
Let the calamity from 60,000 years ago

25:14.430 --> 25:16.230
end today!

25:16.600 --> 25:18.960
Don't leave this pain to future generations!

25:19.380 --> 25:20.610
Fan Yue,

25:20.740 --> 25:23.440
you can't trap me!

25:28.810 --> 25:30.220
Do it, Shuo!

25:30.250 --> 25:32.310
Release the true Xing Yue Arrow.

25:32.330 --> 25:34.600
Let's put an end to all of this together!

25:36.510 --> 25:39.460
You're asking me to send you to your death with my own hands.

25:40.010 --> 25:41.970
I bear the Divine Mantle of the Demon Lord

25:42.500 --> 25:44.410
and the responsibility for all living beings.

25:44.690 --> 25:46.330
I'm willing to die.

25:46.600 --> 25:48.850
It's not for the mission bestowed upon me by the Heaven,

25:49.690 --> 25:51.210
but for you,

25:51.870 --> 25:54.820
and for the countless living beings in this world!

25:55.040 --> 25:56.680
I don't know what a deity should do.

25:57.520 --> 25:58.800
But I know this is what I,

25:59.600 --> 26:02.180
Fan Yue, the Demon King of the Polar Region, must do.

26:04.610 --> 26:11.370
‚ôęIf the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers‚ôę

26:10.360 --> 26:11.740
If the Hidden Heart reappears,

26:12.000 --> 26:13.340
the Eastern Continent will definitely be destroyed!

26:12.000 --> 26:17.820
‚ôęThe moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place‚ôę

26:13.530 --> 26:14.700
You know it.

26:15.500 --> 26:17.070
It's the only way.

26:17.600 --> 26:19.060
Draw your bow, Shuo!

26:19.330 --> 26:22.020
‚ôęAs the wind stirs, the clouds gather‚ôę

26:23.180 --> 26:26.530
‚ôęAs the clouds shift, the moon becomes full‚ôę

26:26.830 --> 26:33.250
‚ôęLove is the hardest thing to understand‚ôę

26:34.000 --> 26:40.660
‚ôęI'm finally back to where it all started‚ôę

26:41.420 --> 26:47.840
‚ôęAll the answers are already explained‚ôę

26:49.200 --> 26:51.490
‚ôęI'll owe you all of my life‚ôę

26:52.390 --> 26:55.610
‚ôęBut we're destined to part‚ôę

26:56.370 --> 27:02.430
‚ôęHow can I downplay this?‚ôę

27:02.910 --> 27:05.970
‚ôęWhen you engrave your love into my heart‚ôę

27:06.670 --> 27:09.780
‚ôęWhen my star falls only for you‚ôę

27:10.460 --> 27:12.000
‚ôęWhen the heavens fall‚ôę

27:12.510 --> 27:17.340
‚ôęI can still connect with you through the waning moon‚ôę

27:17.960 --> 27:20.640
‚ôęWhen my pain blurs my eyes‚ôę

27:19.000 --> 27:21.680
I'm willing to exchange my life

27:21.290 --> 27:25.420
‚ôęOut of the countless stars, I see only you‚ôę

27:23.460 --> 27:25.400
for the peace...

27:25.920 --> 27:27.830
of a city!

27:25.950 --> 27:30.540
‚ôęAs you turn into a falling star‚ôę

27:29.960 --> 27:31.480
The world is vast.

27:31.500 --> 27:32.500
The journey ahead is long.

27:33.220 --> 27:34.200
Promise me,

27:34.580 --> 27:36.600
No matter what happens in the future,

27:36.630 --> 27:38.220
you must continue

27:38.580 --> 27:40.260
to live freely like now.

27:41.350 --> 27:43.670
I hope Master lives a long life without worries,

27:43.750 --> 27:45.300
that the Bright Moon Palace

27:45.340 --> 27:46.790
is the best in the Demon Race,

27:46.820 --> 27:48.780
that Cang Shan eats a lot every day,

27:48.810 --> 27:51.330
and that Tian Huo lives with me happily.

27:51.350 --> 27:55.350
Life is the process of going from having nothing

27:55.380 --> 27:57.580
to having nothing again.

27:57.820 --> 27:59.930
I've always loved freedom.

27:59.950 --> 28:01.230
Now,

28:01.700 --> 28:04.270
I'm finally free.

28:04.600 --> 28:05.920
I'm like the morning light,

28:05.940 --> 28:07.220
while you are like the stars.

28:07.250 --> 28:08.860
The stars shine brightly

28:08.880 --> 28:10.190
as the moon emerges from the clouds.

28:11.320 --> 28:12.690
You must forever,

28:14.670 --> 28:15.840
always...

28:16.800 --> 28:19.660
be that unbreakable Bai Shuo.

28:20.510 --> 28:21.340
I am just...

28:22.960 --> 28:25.490
going to find them.

28:25.520 --> 28:26.800
In this life,

28:27.470 --> 28:30.560
being able to follow you...

28:32.410 --> 28:34.250
leaves me...

28:35.930 --> 28:37.090
with no regrets.

28:49.850 --> 28:51.460
The sixth Contemplation,

28:51.730 --> 28:53.040
the Contemplation of great love.

29:03.900 --> 29:05.030
It's been 60,000 years,

29:05.060 --> 29:06.040
Shuo.

29:08.030 --> 29:10.160
So many deaths were the price

29:10.420 --> 29:13.140
for this one chance to give him a fatal blow!

29:13.780 --> 29:15.850
Don't waste their sacrifice!

29:17.770 --> 29:18.920
Do it!

29:46.410 --> 29:49.440
‚ôęAcross thousands of miles‚ôę

29:54.410 --> 29:59.030
‚ôęThe pain of parting lingers‚ôę

30:02.060 --> 30:08.780
‚ôę I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days‚ôę

30:10.220 --> 30:15.070
‚ôęFlowers in the wind, sand in the water‚ôę

30:12.240 --> 30:13.160
Fan Yue.

30:18.150 --> 30:23.260
‚ôęWhat kind of tree never takes root?‚ôę

30:25.910 --> 30:31.320
‚ôęWhat kind of roots never turn into trees?‚ôę

30:32.940 --> 30:34.490
It doesn't hurt.

30:33.980 --> 30:41.290
‚ôęTo break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart‚ôę

30:35.420 --> 30:37.070
How could you

30:38.960 --> 30:41.180
make me make such a decision?

30:41.940 --> 30:46.730
‚ôęI'm your wanderer‚ôę

30:47.910 --> 30:49.600
The Shuo I know

30:50.170 --> 30:54.700
‚ôęThe flowers flew away‚ôę

30:50.230 --> 30:52.400
is the bravest person in the world.

30:52.440 --> 30:53.980
In the future,

30:54.610 --> 30:56.910
you'll live well, right?

30:57.870 --> 31:03.590
‚ôęMy tears are streaming down like rain‚ôę

31:06.580 --> 31:13.460
‚ôęLight my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world‚ôę

31:14.410 --> 31:20.260
‚ôęOn the vast sea, you and I‚ôę

31:24.670 --> 31:26.390
Are you leaving?

31:37.360 --> 31:38.430
Shuo,

31:40.710 --> 31:41.860
the wind is rising.

32:03.790 --> 32:07.620
‚ôęThe flowers flew away‚ôę

32:10.390 --> 32:11.590
Shuo.

32:11.150 --> 32:16.410
‚ôęMy tears are streaming down like rain‚ôę

32:12.820 --> 32:14.100
I will always be with you.

32:16.040 --> 32:17.860
I'll turn into stars,

32:19.080 --> 32:20.510
into the sun and moon,

32:19.310 --> 32:26.000
‚ôęLight my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world‚ôę

32:22.550 --> 32:24.870
into every breeze

32:25.860 --> 32:27.670
that passes by your side,

32:27.000 --> 32:33.050
‚ôęOn the vast sea, you and I‚ôę

32:29.180 --> 32:31.840
always staying with you.

32:32.470 --> 32:33.790
Shuo.

32:35.300 --> 32:37.270
I love you.

32:37.900 --> 32:39.800
‚ôęMay I ask, what do the gods see in the world?‚ôę

32:40.010 --> 32:42.100
‚ôęSadness from infatuation, anger, and parting‚ôę

32:42.160 --> 32:43.950
‚ôęMy love brought tears‚ôę

32:44.200 --> 32:45.920
‚ôęGreed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness‚ôę

32:46.340 --> 32:48.170
‚ôęI was never a flower, but I withered on my own‚ôę

32:48.380 --> 32:49.800
‚ôęI fell between your brows and became a good fruit‚ôę

32:50.010 --> 32:51.690
‚ôęThe grand dream of life is hard to let go‚ôę

32:52.000 --> 32:53.980
‚ôęSearching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing‚ôę

32:54.340 --> 32:55.920
‚ôęWith a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions‚ôę

32:56.170 --> 32:57.820
‚ôęI cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon‚ôę

32:58.090 --> 33:00.200
‚ôęThe daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright‚ôę

33:00.510 --> 33:02.090
‚ôęThrough the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky‚ôę

33:12.430 --> 33:14.080
I used to think

33:14.100 --> 33:15.670
that Jing Lei was impulsive

33:16.220 --> 33:18.460
and always making noise in my ears.

33:18.750 --> 33:20.430
Now that he's gone,

33:20.460 --> 33:22.170
I find it a bit lonely.

33:22.570 --> 33:23.360
I'm not used to it.

33:26.610 --> 33:28.300
I'm still here.

33:28.330 --> 33:29.330
Before, with Jing Lei around,

33:29.350 --> 33:30.940
there was no chance for me to show myself.

33:30.970 --> 33:31.940
As long as you like,

33:31.960 --> 33:32.710
I can

33:32.740 --> 33:34.440
chatter in your ear all day,

33:34.440 --> 33:35.960
making it so noisy that you can't enjoy your food

33:35.960 --> 33:36.880
or sleep at night.

33:36.880 --> 33:38.160
Alright.

33:38.650 --> 33:40.280
You two are now the two Sect Leaders

33:40.310 --> 33:42.680
jointly in charge of Lanling.

33:42.700 --> 33:44.940
It's inappropriate to bicker all day.

33:45.660 --> 33:47.480
No, no.

33:48.200 --> 33:51.400
From now on, there will be no Sect Leader in Lanling.

33:51.420 --> 33:53.560
The three of us will supervise each other

33:53.590 --> 33:55.910
and jointly protect the world.

33:56.060 --> 33:57.370
That's true.

33:57.390 --> 33:58.590
The key responsibility of the Eternals

33:58.620 --> 33:59.790
lies in establishing the right way,

33:59.810 --> 34:01.360
not in seeking power.

34:01.550 --> 34:03.310
The Eternals finally found peace.

34:04.200 --> 34:05.760
It's just a pity

34:05.820 --> 34:07.770
that Chong Zhao will never come back.

34:09.770 --> 34:12.210
Perhaps this is just how things are in the world‚ÄĒ

34:12.230 --> 34:13.630
rarely perfect.

34:15.710 --> 34:17.469
In this turmoil of the Hidden Lord,

34:17.540 --> 34:19.420
all the races worked together.

34:19.449 --> 34:22.090
In fact, whether they are Eternals, demons, humans,

34:22.110 --> 34:23.310
or Outlanders,

34:23.659 --> 34:26.179
as long as they have a heart to protect all living beings,

34:26.210 --> 34:27.440
they are our kindred spirits

34:28.139 --> 34:31.540
and should be respected by Lanling.

34:32.980 --> 34:34.380
But if you ask me,

34:34.409 --> 34:36.760
the one who deserves respect the most

34:36.780 --> 34:38.300
is Bai Shuo.

34:38.330 --> 34:39.639
Over the past 60,000 years,

34:39.670 --> 34:40.860
who would have thought that

34:40.880 --> 34:43.020
a mortal could become a deity?

34:43.469 --> 34:44.800
A deity

34:44.820 --> 34:47.050
is not defined by how high one's spiritual power is

34:47.080 --> 34:49.550
or by bloodlines,

34:49.590 --> 34:51.070
but by

34:51.100 --> 34:53.280
having a great heart full of love.

34:54.280 --> 34:56.650
Although Bai Shuo inherited the Divine Mantle of Supreme Deity Xing Yue,

34:57.090 --> 34:59.050
she did not become Supreme Deity Xing Yue.

34:59.620 --> 35:03.000
Instead, with her own strength, she became Supreme Deity Bai Shuo

35:03.610 --> 35:05.250
and forged

35:05.270 --> 35:07.240
her own path.

35:05.590 --> 35:08.050
[Tomb of My Father, Bai Xun]

35:14.940 --> 35:18.860
[Tomb of My Father, Bai Xun]

35:15.300 --> 35:16.410
Father,

35:17.420 --> 35:18.810
I've come to see you.

35:23.170 --> 35:24.560
This is a 50-year-old wine.

35:26.110 --> 35:28.180
I took it from the wine cellar of the Unbridled Pavilion.

35:27.920 --> 35:30.530
[Tomb of My Father, Bai Xun]

35:28.880 --> 35:30.360
Let's try it together.

35:45.570 --> 35:46.490
Father,

35:47.660 --> 35:49.260
I miss you.

36:03.360 --> 36:04.390
Good wine!

36:08.860 --> 36:10.010
Little brat,

36:10.550 --> 36:11.550
I'll drink with you.

36:18.080 --> 36:19.440
Father.

36:19.780 --> 36:21.010
I'm here.

36:21.650 --> 36:23.400
I found Xi.

36:24.390 --> 36:25.470
I know.

36:26.180 --> 36:28.370
But I failed to protect her.

36:30.100 --> 36:32.140
That was Xi's choice.

36:31.000 --> 36:34.600
‚ôęDon't linger, don't regret‚ôę

36:32.240 --> 36:33.520
It's not your fault.

36:34.710 --> 36:35.860
By the way,

36:35.420 --> 36:37.890
‚ôęThe last moonlight‚ôę

36:37.430 --> 36:38.760
you've been away from home for so long.

36:38.780 --> 36:39.930
How is it?

36:38.810 --> 36:42.430
‚ôęThe water from my hometown flows gently‚ôę

36:39.960 --> 36:41.330
Have you become an Eternal?

36:43.690 --> 36:45.870
You still remember that?

36:43.810 --> 36:46.410
‚ôęSending me to the distant place‚ôę

36:46.890 --> 36:48.100
I was...

36:46.920 --> 36:50.930
‚ôęIn this life, at this time‚ôę

36:48.940 --> 36:52.160
insincere and fell into demonic ways,

36:51.270 --> 36:54.740
‚ôęI dare not look back‚ôę

36:52.720 --> 36:54.050
so I couldn't become an Eternal.

36:55.040 --> 36:56.440
So be it.

36:55.520 --> 36:58.890
‚ôęIs there the same moonlight‚ôę

36:56.440 --> 36:57.850
It's not a big deal.

36:57.880 --> 36:59.690
Being a happy mortal

36:59.710 --> 37:00.980
is also a good thing.

36:59.920 --> 37:03.090
‚ôęOn your path?‚ôę

37:01.690 --> 37:02.650
Father,

37:03.740 --> 37:06.090
I've seen the world

37:03.800 --> 37:06.960
‚ôęI'm walking on a never-ending long road‚ôę

37:06.700 --> 37:07.860
I once yearned for.

37:07.370 --> 37:10.780
‚ôęIn the vast world, how can I get there?‚ôę

37:08.220 --> 37:10.140
Along the way,

37:10.170 --> 37:11.770
I've loved,

37:11.490 --> 37:13.540
‚ôęIn the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped‚ôę

37:11.870 --> 37:13.520
and been loved.

37:14.000 --> 37:15.830
‚ôęThe moonlight is gentle‚ôę

37:14.150 --> 37:16.200
But now they are all gone.

37:16.350 --> 37:19.440
‚ôęAll the feelings turned into nothing but a dream‚ôę

37:17.750 --> 37:20.520
I've reached the pinnacle of this world,

37:20.150 --> 37:23.420
‚ôęReminiscing about the good old days‚ôę

37:21.930 --> 37:24.640
becoming the strongest person in it.

37:23.640 --> 37:26.930
‚ôęSinging until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost‚ôę

37:24.880 --> 37:27.250
But the price was too high.

37:27.320 --> 37:29.640
‚ôęForget all about the past and leave it behind‚ôę

37:28.260 --> 37:30.000
If I could choose,

37:30.360 --> 37:32.230
I would rather have never left

37:30.370 --> 37:31.700
‚ôęTime after time‚ôę

37:32.320 --> 37:34.080
this little Ning'an City.

37:32.460 --> 37:37.650
‚ôęOh, melancholy‚ôę

37:35.630 --> 37:38.190
I would rather just be Bai Shuo.

37:38.660 --> 37:40.530
I've seen everything

37:41.710 --> 37:43.300
you've been through.

37:44.370 --> 37:45.410
Shuo,

37:46.710 --> 37:48.880
you've done really well.

37:49.930 --> 37:50.710
You must believe

37:50.710 --> 37:52.850
that those who once stood by your side,

37:52.880 --> 37:54.530
even though they've left,

37:54.940 --> 37:57.190
will always stay in your heart.

37:58.840 --> 38:00.130
Just like me,

38:00.520 --> 38:02.240
though I've gone,

38:02.740 --> 38:04.840
no matter when or where,

38:05.130 --> 38:06.410
I'll always be with you.

38:17.480 --> 38:20.520
‚ôęI'm walking on a never-ending long road‚ôę

38:21.050 --> 38:24.190
‚ôęIn the vast world, how can I get there?‚ôę

38:25.410 --> 38:26.580
‚ôęIn the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped‚ôę

38:27.680 --> 38:28.580
‚ôęThe moonlight is gentle‚ôę

38:29.080 --> 38:32.430
‚ôęAll the feelings turned into nothing but a dream‚ôę

38:30.050 --> 38:31.450
Father,

38:32.090 --> 38:33.140
don't worry.

38:33.380 --> 38:36.580
‚ôęReminiscing about the good old days‚ôę

38:34.410 --> 38:35.700
I will walk

38:36.410 --> 38:38.230
this path well.

38:37.050 --> 38:40.150
‚ôęSinging until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost‚ôę

38:41.000 --> 38:42.870
‚ôęForget all about the past and leave it behind‚ôę

39:18.590 --> 39:20.050
Have you understood?

39:23.420 --> 39:25.270
Today, I am touched by your sincerity, as true as that

39:25.290 --> 39:26.250
which can be witnessed by the sun and moon.

39:26.280 --> 39:28.720
I can confidently tell you

39:28.740 --> 39:32.020
the true identity of the guide.

40:02.200 --> 40:03.350
Master Sun?

40:06.500 --> 40:07.770
You are not a mortal.

40:07.840 --> 40:10.400
Even I cannot see through your power.

40:10.420 --> 40:11.650
Who exactly are you?

40:11.900 --> 40:13.110
Who am I?

40:13.530 --> 40:14.930
60,000 years ago,

40:14.960 --> 40:16.440
on the Lunar Hidden Sea,

40:16.460 --> 40:18.460
didn't you ask me the same question?

40:22.380 --> 40:23.370
You are...

40:23.540 --> 40:25.580
I am neither a being of this world

40:25.600 --> 40:27.750
nor a deity of this world.

40:27.870 --> 40:29.680
I have had many names,

40:29.700 --> 40:32.930
but perhaps the one you're most familiar with

40:33.740 --> 40:34.850
is Heaven.

40:43.230 --> 40:45.380
Back when we were in Ning'an City,

40:45.410 --> 40:47.010
you knew who I was?

40:47.030 --> 40:48.320
That's right.

40:48.350 --> 40:51.190
I knew that the Hidden Lord would return to the world,

40:51.210 --> 40:54.000
and I knew you possessed the Divine Mantle of Supreme Deity Xing Yue.

40:54.030 --> 40:55.060
So,

40:55.080 --> 40:59.130
I guided you to meet the Demon Lord once again.

41:01.060 --> 41:02.500
Since you've been here all along,

41:02.520 --> 41:04.350
why didn't you kill Mo Li?

41:04.380 --> 41:05.760
Why did you stand by and watch

41:05.760 --> 41:07.760
so many sacrifices and departures happen?

41:07.820 --> 41:10.530
Heaven is the law of this world

41:11.060 --> 41:14.060
and cannot directly interfere in worldly matters.

41:14.080 --> 41:16.080
Even though I knew Mo Li's evil,

41:16.140 --> 41:18.340
I couldn't completely erase him.

41:18.520 --> 41:20.170
So I awakened you

41:20.200 --> 41:21.820
to protect this world.

41:21.850 --> 41:23.770
And in the end, you did it.

41:23.790 --> 41:24.750
Bai Shuo,

41:24.780 --> 41:26.450
you didn't become Xing Yue.

41:26.710 --> 41:29.570
Instead, you became a deity with the body of a mortal,

41:29.600 --> 41:33.000
the only exception in the world over the past ten thousand years.

41:33.020 --> 41:35.090
You also proved to me

41:35.120 --> 41:36.430
that Heaven

41:36.450 --> 41:37.660
can be wrong too.

41:38.620 --> 41:39.780
I once believed

41:39.800 --> 41:41.640
that by forcing Xing Yue to have no love,

41:41.670 --> 41:43.630
she would become the strongest

41:43.660 --> 41:45.410
and could prevent the catastrophe.

41:46.340 --> 41:47.590
But I failed.

41:48.520 --> 41:50.320
Now, I see

41:50.350 --> 41:52.640
a stronger power in you.

41:53.550 --> 41:54.720
This power

41:54.740 --> 41:55.930
is love,

41:55.960 --> 41:58.560
sacrifice, and protection.

41:59.310 --> 42:01.910
What's the point of telling me that Heaven

42:01.930 --> 42:03.330
has made a mistake now?

42:03.670 --> 42:06.250
Can you undo everything that has happened,

42:06.320 --> 42:09.410
or bring back those who have already passed?

42:10.030 --> 42:11.680
In this world, cause and effect,

42:11.710 --> 42:13.420
good and evil, all have their due.

42:13.440 --> 42:16.610
For love, one can die, but can also be reborn.

42:16.640 --> 42:18.610
Those who died for the great cause

42:18.640 --> 42:21.240
will eventually return

42:21.260 --> 42:22.220
in another way.

42:23.050 --> 42:25.010
Consider it Heaven's way

42:25.220 --> 42:28.080
of compensating for the world.

43:01.260 --> 43:02.310
Remember,

43:02.470 --> 43:04.090
the essence of a deity

43:04.110 --> 43:05.610
is in protection.

43:06.110 --> 43:08.890
Only true and great love

43:08.920 --> 43:11.140
can form an undying power,

43:11.170 --> 43:13.130
crossing all boundaries,

43:13.150 --> 43:15.160
overcoming all evil,

43:15.560 --> 43:17.870
and forever existing with the world.

43:21.820 --> 43:22.860
Shuo!

43:46.520 --> 43:48.110
I'm back, Shuo.

43:46.790 --> 43:50.130
‚ôęThe person standing far away‚ôę

43:51.140 --> 43:52.920
‚ôęDon't be afraid‚ôę

43:54.080 --> 43:58.220
‚ôęThe stars will guide you to me‚ôę

43:59.170 --> 44:05.390
‚ôęWalk towards me‚ôę

43:59.290 --> 44:01.000
These days,

44:01.020 --> 44:02.980
I have been to many places

44:04.360 --> 44:06.000
to see

44:07.100 --> 44:09.050
the magnificent sights you mentioned.

44:07.580 --> 44:10.250
‚ôęMy heart feels so...‚ôę

44:09.510 --> 44:11.000
The sun, moon, stars,

44:10.920 --> 44:16.530
‚ôęIt's pounding as I wait for you‚ôę

44:11.180 --> 44:12.900
drifting clouds, and gentle breeze.

44:13.160 --> 44:15.580
I saw everything as traces of you,

44:16.350 --> 44:18.140
as if you were right by my side.

44:18.740 --> 44:22.400
‚ôęThe stars light up your eyes‚ôę

44:19.970 --> 44:21.990
But you always came with the wind

44:22.540 --> 44:24.000
and faded away with it.

44:26.240 --> 44:29.390
‚ôęYou are my distant call‚ôę

44:26.400 --> 44:27.340
I know

44:28.250 --> 44:30.170
those were never truly you.

44:30.070 --> 44:34.120
‚ôęYou are my first and last‚ôę

44:31.770 --> 44:33.300
Is the you

44:34.560 --> 44:35.720
before me now real?

44:35.270 --> 44:41.000
‚ôęMy heart is trembling for you‚ôę

44:38.650 --> 44:39.400
Shuo,

44:40.400 --> 44:42.900
this time, I'll use my whole life to answer you.

44:41.570 --> 44:44.400
‚ôęIn this moment where we embrace each other‚ôę

44:45.420 --> 44:48.040
‚ôęLet's never let go‚ôę

44:55.870 --> 44:56.760
Fan Yue,

44:57.080 --> 44:58.210
the wind is rising.

45:07.420 --> 45:09.170
It's not the wind.

45:10.700 --> 45:11.970
It's my heartbeat.

45:12.170 --> 45:15.410
‚ôęWhen you engrave your love into my heart‚ôę

45:16.090 --> 45:18.250
‚ôęWhen my star falls only for you‚ôę

45:19.350 --> 45:20.510
‚ôęWhen the heavens fall‚ôę

45:21.550 --> 45:25.810
‚ôęI can still connect with you through the waning moon‚ôę

45:26.840 --> 45:29.450
‚ôęWhen my pain blurs my eyes‚ôę

45:30.560 --> 45:34.230
‚ôęOut of the countless stars, I see only you‚ôę

45:35.180 --> 45:45.040
‚ôęAs you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart‚ôę

45:41.250 --> 45:42.180
Fan Yue,

45:43.300 --> 45:44.890
thank you for coming back.

45:56.110 --> 45:59.510
[The End]
